  <brief_title>New Ways to Help Patients Improve Their Diabetes Control</brief_title>
  <official_title>Examining Ways to Increase Patient Understanding of Diabetes Control and Disease Severity Through Reinterpretation of Hemoglobin A1C Values With the Goal of Improved Diabetes Control</official_title>
