    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        1. Patients over the age of 18 with diabetes mellitus listed as a problem list or in their
        past medical history on their electronic medical record who have a hemoglobin A1C value
        greater than 8% within three months of study enrollment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Pregnant patients

          2. Illiterate patients

          3. Patients with known cognitive deficits affecting ability to participate in study

          4. Any current participants in another active research study
      </textblock>
